::Mosquitor::

Mosquitor opens his eyes. He seemed to be laying in some hallway. In a very 
uncomfortable position, and in a great deal of pain. He groans, attempting to 
get up, and failing as his legs give out.

Mosquitor groans again, dragging himself toward the CR chambers.
